results.name: Total weight of the multiset of multisets of multisets with MMM number n. Totally additive with a(prime(n)) = A302242(n).
comment: A prime index of n is a number m such that prime(m) divides n. The multiset of prime indices of n is row n of A112798. The finite multiset of finite multisets of finite multisets of positive integers with MMM number n is obtained by factoring n into prime numbers, then factoring each of their prime indices into prime numbers, then factoring each of their prime indices into prime numbers, and finally taking their prime indices.
